<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.10.5">
<l>mūḷa vericinti muṉiveyti yamarceytu meṉavanta vacurar</l>
<l>tōḷu mavartāḷu muṭiyōṭu poṭiyāka noṭiyāma ḷaveytāṉ</l>
<l>vāḷum varivillum vaḷaiyāḻi kataicaṅka mivaiyaṅkai yuṭaiyāṉ</l>
<l>nāḷu muṟaikiṉṟa nakarnanti puraviṇṇa karamnaṇṇu maṉamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O heart, go to Nantipura Viṇṇakaram, the city where daily dwells</l>
<l>The one who has in his fine hands these: a sword, striped bow, round discus,</l>
<l rend="indent">mace, and conch,</l>
<l>The one who shot [arrows] scattering fire so it kindled [Laṅkā],</l>
<l rend="indent">so that the arms, legs, and heads of the demons,</l>
<l>Who came, [their] rage rising, as they said, “We will make war,”</l>
<l rend="indent">became ash in the measure of a second.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
